snippet.title: Summer Wells Crime Lab Van & White Tent Is Out Today During Search For Summer Wells @Crackin’ Cases
snippet.description:
I follow “Crack Cases” YouTube channel & ran across this video of theirs about the Summer Wells case.

It is about there being searchers out near her home today to search for her, again incase they missed her the times they’ve searched for her there the first time. 

They have a crime lab van & a white tent put up. Does this mean they found something? 

From what I learned about the Gabby Petito case when they found Brian Laundrie’s remains, a professional had said that they absolutely will not bring this van out here unless human remains were found & same goes for the tent I believe, don’t quote me on this.

Just like the Brian Laundrie case, they set up a white tent & a crime lab van of some kind came out, I can’t confirm if it is the same kind, so please do not quote me on this. 

I am not saying or confirming that they have found her, or something to do with Summer Wells case that is very crucial to her & her case, but, I am saying that from what I heard in this video, they do have a crime lab van out there & a white tent.

I don’t know what for, so, go to Crack Cases channel, & subscribe to their channel to get all of the updates about this, such as Ronnie Lawson going to make a statement soon, as I also heard from Crackin Cases. 

WATCH THIS FULL VIDEO HERE: https://youtu.be/8KVkGRaV8js

*Video credits go to “Crack Cases”.

Subscribe to their channel here: https://youtube.com/c/Crackin%E2%80%99Cases
